Calculators
Single Calculators hub page with tabs or cards for each tool, similar to bank affordability tools.
​

Mortgage Payment Calculator

Inputs:

Home price or loan amount

Down payment

Interest rate

Term (years)

Taxes, insurance, HOA (optional)

Outputs:

Monthly principal & interest

Estimated total monthly payment

Amortization summary.

Affordability Calculator

Inputs (like U.S. Bank / PNC tools):
​

Annual income

Monthly debt payments

Down payment amount

State = Pennsylvania

Desired DTI / comfort level slider (Conservative / Moderate / Aggressive)

Outputs:

“Estimated max home price”

Estimated monthly mortgage

A range: Conservative / Stretch / Aggressive.

Refinance Calculator

Inputs:

Current loan balance, rate, remaining term, current monthly payment.

New rate & term options.

Estimated closing costs.

Outputs:

New monthly payment vs current.

Monthly savings.

Breakeven in months.

CTA under results:

“Discuss my numbers with Team MAI” → Apply/meeting.

