Preferred contact time.

Style / UX notes
Visual direction:

Roman royal purple as primary, with gold/cream accent for luxury feel (consistent with your branding preference).

Clean, Movement-style card layouts for programs and calculators.
​

UX:

Anchor links from Home to each section.

Clear CTAs at bottom of every page/section: “Schedule a Call”, “Start My Approval”.

Mobile-first design; calculators and program cards stack cleanly.
